nd": 157.02, "text": " It gives us real oversight, not just a plausible story.", "tokens": [51336, 467, 2709, 505, 957, 29146, 11, 406, 445, 257, 39925, 1657, 13, 51473], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.22389683442957262, "compression_ratio": 1.5319148936170213, "no_speech_prob": 1.5189513058802562e-12}, {"id": 42, "seek": 15702, "start": 157.02, "end": 164.82000000000002, "text": " Okay. So calm sounds like a path towards, well, deeper and more trustworthy AI. But how deep does", "tokens": [50365, 1033, 13, 407, 7151, 3263, 411, 257, 3100, 3030, 11, 731, 11, 7731, 293, 544, 39714, 7318, 13, 583, 577, 2452, 775, 50755], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06633512377738952, "compression_ratio": 1.4455445544554455, "no_speech_prob": 1.455295085828201e-12}, {"id": 43, "seek": 15702, "start": 164.82000000000002, "end": 169.36, "text": " this idea of AI memory go? Is it just storing data or is there more to it?", "tokens": [50755, 341, 1558, 295, 7318, 4675, 352, 30, 1119, 309, 445, 26085, 1412, 420, 307, 456, 544, 281, 309, 30, 50982], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06633512377738952, "compression_ratio": 1.4455445544554455, "no_speech_prob": 1.455295085828201e-12}, {"id": 44, "seek": 15702, "start": 169.42000000000002, "end": 173.78, "text": " Oh, it can go much, much deeper. It starts connecting to some really advanced, almost physics-like", "tokens": [50985, 876, 11, 309, 393, 352, 709, 11, 709, 7731, 13, 467, 3719, 11015, 281, 512, 534, 7339, 11, 1920, 10649, 12, 4092, 51203], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06633512377738952, "compression_ratio": 1.4455445544554455, "no_speech_prob": 1.455295085828201e-12}, {"id": 45, "seek": 15702, "start": 173.78, "end": 174.38, "text": " concepts.", "tokens": [51203, 10392, 13, 51233], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06633512377738952, "compression_ratio": 1.4455445544554455, "no_speech_prob": 1.455295085828201e-12}, {"id": 46, "seek": 15702, "start": 174.62, "end": 175.0, "text": " Like what?", "tokens": [51245, 1743, 437, 30, 51264], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06633512377738952, "compression_ratio": 1.4455445544554455, "no_speech_prob": 1.455295085828201e-12}, {"id": 47, "seek": 17500, "start": 175.0, "end": 179.36, "text": " Well, for instance, in what's called RSVP-based calm, the memory states aren't just static", "tokens": [50365, 1042, 11, 337, 5197, 11, 294, 437, 311, 1219, 25855, 53, 47, 12, 6032, 7151, 11, 264, 4675, 4368, 3212, 380, 445, 13437, 50583], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12236816271216469, "compression_ratio": 1.607773851590106, "no_speech_prob": 1.5365263315164635e-12}, {"id": 48, "seek": 17500, "start": 179.36, "end": 182.72, "text": " points. They're more like points in a dynamic field, constantly adjusting.", "tokens": [50583, 2793, 13, 814, 434, 544, 411, 2793, 294, 257, 8546, 2519, 11, 6460, 23559, 13, 50751], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12236816271216469, "compression_ratio": 1.607773851590106, "no_speech_prob": 1.5365263315164635e-12}, {"id": 49, "seek": 17500, "start": 182.76, "end": 184.06, "text": " A field, like in physics.", "tokens": [50753, 316, 2519, 11, 411, 294, 10649, 13, 50818], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12236816271216469, "compression_ratio": 1.607773851590106, "no_speech_prob": 1.5365263315164635e-12}, {"id": 50, "seek": 17500, "start": 184.16, "end": 188.24, "text": " Sort of analogous, yeah. The internal dynamics are governed by principles that ensure coherence,", "tokens": [50823, 26149, 295, 16660, 563, 11, 1338, 13, 440, 6920, 15679, 366, 35529, 538, 9156, 300, 5586, 26528, 655, 11, 51027], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12236816271216469, "compression_ratio": 1.607773851590106, "no_speech_prob": 1.5365263315164635e-12}, {"id": 51, "seek": 17500, "start": 188.56, "end": 193.16, "text": " like thermodynamic and structural stability. It's about maintaining a consistent internal", "tokens": [51043, 411, 8810, 34988, 293, 15067, 11826, 13, 467, 311, 466, 14916, 257, 8398, 6920, 51273], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12236816271216469, "compression_ratio": 1.607773851590106, "no_speech_prob": 1.5365263315164635e-12}, {"id": 52, "seek": 17500, "start": 193.16, "end": 194.6, "text": " world or memory landscape.", "tokens": [51273, 1002, 420, 4675, 9661, 13, 51345], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12236816271216469, "compression_ratio": 1.607773851590106, "no_speech_prob": 1.5365263315164635e-12}, {"id": 53, "seek": 17500, "start": 195.0, "end": 197.52, "text": " Wow. Okay. And you mentioned another one, Tartan.", "tokens": [51365, 3153, 13, 1033, 13, 400, 291, 2835, 1071, 472, 11, 314, 446, 282, 13, 51491], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.12236816271216469, "compression_ratio": 1.607773851590106, "no_speech_prob": 1.5365263315164635e-12}, {"id": 54, "seek": 19752, "start": 197.52, "end": 202.78, "text": " Right. Tartan takes things even further by integrating something called oscillatory semantics.", "tokens": [50365, 1779, 13, 314, 446, 282, 2516, 721, 754, 3052, 538, 26889, 746, 1219, 18225, 4745, 4361, 45298, 13, 50628], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11581527141102574, "compression_ratio": 1.6629213483146068, "no_speech_prob": 1.6171620249513796e-12}, {"id": 55, "seek": 19752, "start": 203.36, "end": 204.42000000000002, "text": " This is pretty mind-bending.", "tokens": [50657, 639, 307, 1238, 1575, 12, 65, 2029, 13, 50710], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11581527141102574, "compression_ratio": 1.6629213483146068, "no_speech_prob": 1.6171620249513796e-12}, {"id": 56, "seek": 19752, "start": 204.74, "end": 205.92000000000002, "text": " Oscillatory semantics.", "tokens": [50726, 17406, 373, 4745, 4361, 45298, 13, 50785], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11581527141102574, "compression_ratio": 1.6629213483146068, "no_speech_prob": 1.6171620249513796e-12}, {"id": 57, "seek": 19752, "start": 206.20000000000002, "end": 211.04000000000002, "text": " It interprets even stillness, the absence of change, as a dynamic state, like a subtle", "tokens": [50799, 467, 17489, 1373, 754, 920, 1287, 11, 264, 17145, 295, 1319, 11, 382, 257, 8546, 1785, 11, 411, 257, 13743, 51041], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11581527141102574, "compression_ratio": 1.6629213483146068, "no_speech_prob": 1.6171620249513796e-12}, {"id": 58, "seek": 19752, "start": 211.04000000000002, "end": 217.06, "text": " oscillation. It means tiny, tiny micro-movements or patterns within the AI's internal state", "tokens": [51041, 18225, 399, 13, 467, 1355, 5870, 11, 5870, 4532, 12, 76, 1682, 1117, 420, 8294, 1951, 264, 7318, 311, 6920, 1785, 51342], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11581527141102574, "compression_ratio": 1.6629213483146068, "no_speech_prob": 1.6171620249513796e-12}, {"id": 59, "seek": 19752, "start": 217.06, "end": 220.76000000000002, "text": " can encode really complex embodied abstractions.", "tokens": [51342, 393, 2058, 1429, 534, 3997, 42046, 12649, 626, 13, 51527], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11581527141102574, "compression_ratio": 1.6629213483146068, "no_speech_prob": 1.6171620249513796e-12}, {"id": 60, "seek": 19752, "start": 220.84, "end": 225.74, "text": " So like reading meaning from a tiny twitch, or even no twitch at all.", "tokens": [51531, 407, 411, 3760, 3620, 490, 257, 5870, 34167, 11, 420, 754, 572, 34167, 412, 439, 13, 51776], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11581527141102574, "compression_ratio": 1.6629213483146068, "no_speech_prob": 1.6171620249513796e-12}, {"id": 61, "seek": 22574, "start": 225.74, "end": 231.14000000000001, "text": " Exactly. Forming what they call cognitive glyphs. Imagine an AI understanding nuance from something", "tokens": [50365, 7587, 13, 10126, 278, 437, 436, 818, 15605, 22633, 950, 82, 13, 11739, 364, 7318, 3701, 42625, 490, 746, 50635], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09798034280538559, "compression_ratio": 1.5389221556886228, "no_speech_prob": 1.4215829034769367e-12}, {"id": 62, "seek": 22574, "start": 231.14000000000001, "end": 235.8, "text": " as subtle as a slight shift in posture, or the lack of an expected micro-movement. It's", "tokens": [50635, 382, 13743, 382, 257, 4036, 5513, 294, 18502, 11, 420, 264, 5011, 295, 364, 5176, 4532, 12, 76, 1682, 518, 13, 467, 311, 50868], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09798034280538559, "compression_ratio": 1.5389221556886228, "no_speech_prob": 1.4215829034769367e-12}, {"id": 63, "seek": 22574, "start": 235.8, "end": 238.0, "text": " a much deeper level of semantic understanding.", "tokens": [50868, 257, 709, 7731, 1496, 295, 47982, 3701, 13, 50978], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09798034280538559, "compression_ratio": 1.5389221556886228, "no_speech_prob": 1.4215829034769367e-12}, {"id": 64, "seek": 22574, "start": 238.28, "end": 242.34, "text": " Yeah, that's pretty profound. So where does all this lead? We have calm for traceable reasoning,", "tokens": [50992, 865, 11, 300, 311, 1238, 14382, 13, 407, 689, 775, 439, 341, 1477, 30, 492, 362, 7151, 337, 13508, 712, 21577, 11, 51195], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09798034280538559, "compression_ratio": 1.5389221556886228, "no_speech_prob": 1.4215829034769367e-12}, {"id": 65, "seek": 22574, "start": 242.58, "end": 247.38, "text": " RSVP for dynamic memory fields, Tartan for deep semantics. Are these being combined?", "tokens": [51207, 25855, 53, 47, 337, 8546, 4675, 7909, 11, 314, 446, 282, 337, 2452, 4361, 45298, 13, 2014, 613, 885, 9354, 30, 51447], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09798034280538559, "compression_ratio": 1.5389221556886228, "no_speech_prob": 1.4215829034769367e-12}, {"id": 66, "seek": 22574, "start": 247.56, "end": 251.92000000000002, "text": " They are. Researchers are working on unified architectures. One example mentioned is Heishwydere.", "tokens": [51456, 814, 366, 13, 43555, 366, 1364, 322, 26787, 6331, 1303, 13, 1485, 1365, 2835, 307, 634, 742, 86, 6655, 323, 13, 51674], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.09798034280538559, "compression_ratio": 1.5389221556886228, "no_speech_prob": 1.4215829034769367e-12}, {"id": 67, "seek": 25192, "start": 251.92, "end": 258.24, "text": " Yeah. It aims to bring together personalization, aspects of neurocognitive realism. So mimicking", "tokens": [50365, 865, 13, 467, 24683, 281, 1565, 1214, 2973, 2144, 11, 7270, 295, 16499, 66, 2912, 2187, 38484, 13, 407, 12247, 10401, 50681], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11974207851864876, "compression_ratio": 1.5845588235294117, "no_speech_prob": 1.7827733646974542e-12}, {"id": 68, "seek": 25192, "start": 258.24, "end": 263.64, "text": " brain functions a bit, comms, causal interpretability, and the kind of deep semantic grounding we see", "tokens": [50681, 3567, 6828, 257, 857, 11, 800, 82, 11, 38755, 7302, 2310, 11, 293, 264, 733, 295, 2452, 47982, 46727, 321, 536, 50951], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11974207851864876, "compression_ratio": 1.5845588235294117, "no_speech_prob": 1.7827733646974542e-12}, {"id": 69, "seek": 25192, "start": 263.64, "end": 265.14, "text": " in RSVP and Tartan.", "tokens": [50951, 294, 25855, 53, 47, 293, 314, 446, 282, 13, 51026], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11974207851864876, "compression_ratio": 1.5845588235294117, "no_speech_prob": 1.7827733646974542e-12}, {"id": 70, "seek": 25192, "start": 265.26, "end": 268.76, "text": " So the goal is truly understandable AI.", "tokens": [51032, 407, 264, 3387, 307, 4908, 25648, 7318, 13, 51207], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11974207851864876, "compression_ratio": 1.5845588235294117, "no_speech_prob": 1.7827733646974542e-12}, {"id": 71, "seek": 25192, "start": 269.03999999999996, "end": 274.26, "text": " The goal is AI reasoning that is causally faithful. You can trust its explanation.", "tokens": [51221, 440, 3387, 307, 7318, 21577, 300, 307, 3302, 379, 17808, 13, 509, 393, 3361, 1080, 10835, 13, 51482], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11974207851864876, "compression_ratio": 1.5845588235294117, "no_speech_prob": 1.7827733646974542e-12}, {"id": 72, "seek": 25192, "start": 274.4, "end": 274.56, "text": " Right.", "tokens": [51489, 1779, 13, 51497], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11974207851864876, "compression_ratio": 1.5845588235294117, "no_speech_prob": 1.7827733646974542e-12}, {"id": 73, "seek": 25192, "start": 274.74, "end": 279.28, "text": " It's personalized and deeply grounded in meaning, not just surface level patterns.", "tokens": [51506, 467, 311, 28415, 293, 8760, 23535, 294, 3620, 11, 406, 445, 3753, 1496, 8294, 13, 51733], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.11974207851864876, "compression_ratio": 1.5845588235294117, "no_speech_prob": 1.7827733646974542e-12}, {"id": 74, "seek": 27928, "start": 279.28, "end": 283.71999999999997, "text": " Okay. This is clearly cutting edge stuff, but let's bring it back. Why should you,", "tokens": [50365, 1033, 13, 639, 307, 4448, 6492, 4691, 1507, 11, 457, 718, 311, 1565, 309, 646, 13, 1545, 820, 291, 11, 50587], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10910861864002473, "compression_ratio": 1.5339805825242718, "no_speech_prob": 1.9815403658196562e-12}, {"id": 75, "seek": 27928, "start": 283.96, "end": 290.52, "text": " listening right now, care about this shift? Moving from AI thinking out loud to AI remembering", "tokens": [50599, 4764, 558, 586, 11, 1127, 466, 341, 5513, 30, 14242, 490, 7318, 1953, 484, 6588, 281, 7318, 20719, 50927], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10910861864002473, "compression_ratio": 1.5339805825242718, "no_speech_prob": 1.9815403658196562e-12}, {"id": 76, "seek": 27928, "start": 290.52, "end": 293.02, "text": " and using these complex internal dynamics?", "tokens": [50927, 293, 1228, 613, 3997, 6920, 15679, 30, 51052], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10910861864002473, "compression_ratio": 1.5339805825242718, "no_speech_prob": 1.9815403658196562e-12}, {"id": 77, "seek": 27928, "start": 293.2, "end": 297.15999999999997, "text": " Well, fundamentally, it's about trust and safety. This whole direction moves us towards AI systems", "tokens": [51061, 1042, 11, 17879, 11, 309, 311, 466, 3361, 293, 4514, 13, 639, 1379, 3513, 6067, 505, 3030, 7318, 3652, 51259], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10910861864002473, "compression_ratio": 1.5339805825242718, "no_speech_prob": 1.9815403658196562e-12}, {"id": 78, "seek": 27928, "start": 297.15999999999997, "end": 299.47999999999996, "text": " with genuine epistemic transparency.", "tokens": [51259, 365, 16699, 2388, 468, 3438, 17131, 13, 51375], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10910861864002473, "compression_ratio": 1.5339805825242718, "no_speech_prob": 1.9815403658196562e-12}, {"id": 79, "seek": 27928, "start": 299.76, "end": 300.5, "text": " Knowing how it knows.", "tokens": [51389, 25499, 577, 309, 3255, 13, 51426], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10910861864002473, "compression_ratio": 1.5339805825242718, "no_speech_prob": 1.9815403658196562e-12}, {"id": 80, "seek": 27928, "start": 300.59999999999997, "end": 304.52, "text": " Exactly. Instead of using AI, whose reasoning is effectively a black box where the explanations", "tokens": [51431, 7587, 13, 7156, 295, 1228, 7318, 11, 6104, 21577, 307, 8659, 257, 2211, 2424, 689, 264, 28708, 51627], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10910861864002473, "compression_ratio": 1.5339805825242718, "no_speech_prob": 1.9815403658196562e-12}, {"id": 81, "seek": 30452, "start": 304.52, "end": 308.85999999999996, "text": " cannot be trusted or verified, this path promises AI cognition that's robust,", "tokens": [50365, 2644, 312, 16034, 420, 31197, 11, 341, 3100, 16403, 7318, 46905, 300, 311, 13956, 11, 50582], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.13788020053756572, "compression_ratio": 1.5631399317406143, "no_speech_prob": 2.4751017208002324e-12}, {"id": 82, "seek": 30452, "start": 309.2, "end": 311.7, "text": " more generalizable, and truly interpretable.", "tokens": [50599, 544, 2674, 22395, 11, 293, 4908, 7302, 712, 13, 50724], "temperat